      "writtenOn": "2026-06-29T16:58:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If I am understanding this correctly, the System class will initialize the chassis containing the BMC to present and all the others to not present.\n\nI don\u0027t agree with this. Other firmware (such as VPD collection) may have already set the chassis presence in inventory manager based on GPIOs. So you would be overwriting the correct presence with False. Also, some other applications will take actions based on the value you publish on D-Bus. So we shouldn\u0027t publish false if that is not the correct value (haven\u0027t read GPIO yet).",
      "revId": "9bd5ea7ae711f5fac7dd010635898d144ccce4d8",
